# Requirements (30 Points):

1. Page must use an External CSS File \- 1 pt

The Page must have the following Sections 

2. Header \+ Footer   
   1. This should use the same styling, aka same div class \- 2 pt  
   2. Header should have an H1 \- 1pt  
   3. Text must be aligned to the center of the page \- 1 pt  
   4. that Must be different color than the rest of the page \- 1 pt  
   5. They should have Margin \+ Padding \- 1 pt  
3. Body  
   1. Main Content (This must use a percentage width) \- 2 pt  
   2. Sidebar (This must use a percentage width)  
      1. The color must be different form the rest of the page \- 2 pt  
   3. Both Main Content and sidebar must be within one Line (the Sidebar shouldn't be on a new line vs the main content) \- 2 pt  
   4. Both must have Margin \+ Padding \- 2 pt  
   5. The whole Body should use a custom font-family**,** it is your choice what that is \- 1pt  
4. In the Main Content there must be a form  
   1. The form must have a Name Label \- 1pt  
   2. The form must have a Select that chooses, Rock \- Paper \- Scissors \- 1 pt  
   3. The form must require the name \- 1 pt  
   4. When you focus on the Name Text box the width of the textbox must increase, then when you ‚Äúun-focus‚Äù it should go back to it‚Äôs original length \- 2 pt  
5. SideBar  
   1. The Sidebar must have Rules on how to Play Rock-Paper-Scissors \- 1 pt  
   2. When you hover over the Sidebar it should change the background color \- 2 pts  
6. Nav  
   1. The Nav must have 3 elements, lined up horizontally and with no bullet points \- 3 pt  
   2. The Nav elements must have a hover state \- 1 pt  
   3. The Nav elements when clicked should open up a different site (can be any site) \- 2 pts
